text: Hello Jessica- nice to meet you!
How is your week going so far?
Nice to meet you too
So far so good. And with you?
Pretty great. This weather has been amazing, so I got some time outdoors today.
Nice job keeping it positive. People are generally attracted to positive energy.
Where should we take this conversation?
option_a_text: Figure out why she is on a dating app

text: Have you met any cool people on this app yet?
Hahaha, I've met a few people
But honestly, I mostly use it for entertainment
When I'm bored lol
How about you?
Yeah, I've met some great women on this app
I think meeting new people is one of the best parts of life, so overall I think dating apps are net positive
That's what I'm talking about with positive vibes. Nice work. Let's see how she responds
I totally agree :)
What do you do for work? :)
I work as a clinical assistant for a chronic pain clinic and functional rehab center
What do you do?
Wow. That sounds like a really cool job. How long have you been in healthcare for?
I'm a software engineer
I actually just graduated a year ago. I was an EMT for a little bit and then in this job since then.
That's cool. Did you study engineering in school?
I did, but honestly I learned more outside of school than in school.
It's nice to get to know people. But conversation like this can get really dry talking through an app. Perhaps try another topic?

option_b_text: Ask about her interests and hobbies

text: So what are some of your favorite date activities?
Hahaha
Hmmmm. I like going out to eat. I think most people do haha
How about you?
I like going out to eat as well :) I also like going on hikes, and checking out museums and art shows.
So what do you like to do when you're not working?
Sorry to say, this is where the conversation ends. Next time try asking some questions that are a little more interesting or unexpected.

option_b_text: Ask her to at an event

text: So would you like to go out to dinner sometime?
Sometimes people just don't respond. It's nothing personal. Keep on moving, and maintain a positive attitude.
There's this weekly event at the academy of sciences called nightlife, have you heard of it?
I have not. What is it?
Basically the academy of sciences has all of these cool exhibits and an aquarium, and they do an after hours event on Thursday nights with music and drinks.
It's a pretty fun time
It sounds really neat :)
Would you be open to going this Thursday? Maybe we can get something to eat before or after?
Yeah, that sounds like fun :)
great!
Want to coordinate over text? My number is 555.555.5555.
Sure
My number is 555.555.5555
Sounds like a super fun event, great move offering a unqiue date idea.
Hello there :) This is Colin
Hey Colin :)
How's your evening going?
Pretty well, just at home cooking dinner
Nice! What are you cooking?
Pasta and salad
What are you up to?
Was about to head to the gym actually
Sublte information that displays that you're heathly and well rounded can go a long way.
Nice :)
So for this Thursday, the event goes from 6-10. When is a good time for you?
Hmmmm
I think 7 or 8 would be best
Either works for me. Should we say 7:30?
Also, would you like me to pick you up, or would you like to meet there?
Good move. Sometimes women don't like the idea of a stranger picking them up. It's always nice to offer, but make it an option.
You can pick me up at my place at 7:30.
My address is 1223 Potrero
Great! See you Thursday at 7:30
Your date is coming up tomorrow.
option_a_text: Send a text to check in.

text: Hey Jessica! Still on for tomorrow night?
Yessir :)
Great! I'll see you at 7:30. Looking forward to it.
Me too :)
Hey Jessica! Still on for tonight?
Hey there
Yeah! Looking forward to it.
Me too :)
Thanks for meeting up with me tonight Jessica!
Thank you for dinner :)
You're welcome :)
I hope you have a good night
You too
Okay okay. Seems like you had a decent date. Wait a couple days, and follow up to see how she is and ask her out again.
